    <briefdescription>
<para>\par \b Purpose\/ \:  To convert binary blob files (mime=application/octet-stream) that carry image-like extensions (.bmp, .jpg, .tiff, etc.) into PNG by delegating to PNGConverter. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Converts image-like documents with <computeroutput>mime=application/octet-stream</computeroutput> into PNG. Look to the :class:<computeroutput>~dedoc.converters.AbstractConverter</computeroutput> documentation to get the information about the methods&apos; parameters. </para>
    </detaileddescription>
